| Code in `.trae/skills/` | Apache-2.0 | Use freely with attribution |
| Prompt files in `prompts/` | CC BY 4.0 | Share and adapt with attribution |
| Workflow files | CC BY 4.0 | Share and adapt with attribution |
| Documentation | CC BY 4.0 | Share and adapt with attribution |

